hivis.data

Interface DataSeries.DoubleSeries

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Data, DataSequence, DataSeries<Double>, Iterable<Double>
    Enclosing interface:
    DataSeries<V>

    public static interface DataSeries.DoubleSeries
extends DataSeries<Double>
    Internal use. Interface for DataSeries representing double values. Allows DataSeries.asDouble() to return series that do not lose their generic type due to type erasure.
